description: [``botocore``] This release adds a new API GetContactMetrics for Amazon Connect.
[``botocore``] Add CVSSV4 to Vulnerability Search API and update enable/disable account id list length to 5
[``botocore``] Adding DeleteConnection API to IoT Data Plane
[``botocore``] Adds support for GB200 UltraServers in Amazon SageMaker training jobs, training plans, and HyperPod clusters
[``botocore``] Update documentation to use key ARN only in OutputEncryptionKMSKeyId request parameter
[``botocore``] Fixes a bug which causes the stubber to begin failing for DynamoDB when SSO or AssumeRole credentials fail to load
